text: Sean O'Neill is the name of: * Sean O'Neill (actor) (born 1985), Canadian, actor and arts professional * Seán O'Neill (born 1938), Gaelic football player for Down * Sean O'Neill (Louth Gaelic footballer), Gaelic football player for Louth * Seán O'Neill (hurler) (born 1972), Irish hurler for Limerick * Sean O'Neill (footballer) (born 1988), association footballer * Sean O'Neill (table tennis) (born 1967), American table tennis player and coach * Sean O'Neill (rower) (born 1980), Irish / New Zealand rower ==See also== * Sean O'Neal (born 1977), actor
title: Sean O'Neill
